  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to explore whether and how high circulating levels of endothelin-1
      (ET-1) in obese and overweight children may contribute to impair adiponectin (Ad) production,
      release and vascular activity
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
